h1. params 

h2. Purpose

A mutable multi-dimensional map (hash) of request (CGI) parameters 

h2. Examples

bc.
class BookController {
	def index = {
		flash.message = "Welcome!"
		redirect(action:home)
	}
	def home = {}
}

h2. Description

The standard Servlet API provides access to parameters via the @HttpServletRequest@ object